<div class="scp-image-block block-center scp-clear-false" style="width:700px;"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-2626-jp/Casadh_an_tSugain.jpg" style="width:700px;" alt="Casadh_an_tSugain.jpg" class="image" />
